FBIS3-48816 "dreas020_g_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Burma SLORC Renames Border Areas Ministry BK3001084594 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 0630 GMT 30 Jan 94 BK3001084594 Rangoon Radio Burma Language: Burmese Article Type:BFN ["Notification No. 15/94 of the State Law and Order Restoration Council," issued on 30 Jan 94] [Text] Reorganization of Ministry. For more effective implementation of urban and rural development, the State Law and Order Restoration Council [SLORC] has reorganized the Ministry of Development of Border Areas and National Races as the Ministry of Progress of Border Areas and National Races and Development Affairs. By the authority vested in me, Signed; Khin Nyunt, Lieutenant General, secretary-1 of the SLORC.
